### List all accounts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts
Accept: application/json

###

### Get account by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Update account (name, color, icon)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hauptkonto",
  "color": "#3b82f6",
  "icon": "bank"
}
